taskHint 
Game: ARMA 2  (1.00) 
Description: Shows info about new, changed or failed task. The text can contain 
 several lines. 
 is used to indicate the end of a line.  To maintain 
 Arma 3 visual style, it's recommended to use BIS_fnc_showNotification 
 instead. 
Syntax:  
 taskHint [hintText, [r, g, b, a], icon] 
Parameters: 
[hintText, [r, g, b, a], icon]: Array 
hintText: String 
[r, g, b, a]: Array - format Color 
icon: String - possible values: taskNew, taskDone, taskFailed, taskCurrent 
Return Value: 
 Nothing